292
00:14:46,832 --> 00:14:50,432
NARRATOR: Although individual
ARVN units fought bravely,

293
00:14:50,533 --> 00:14:53,000
the invasion was a failure.

294
00:15:10,666 --> 00:15:14,332
Almost half of the 17,000 South Vietnamese

295
00:15:14,432 --> 00:15:15,865
who entered Laos

296
00:15:15,966 --> 00:15:19,100
would be killed, wounded or captured.

297
00:15:20,700 --> 00:15:24,066
HUE:

298
