472
00:24:40,266 --> 00:24:42,365
"is a disgrace to this nation.

473
00:24:42,465 --> 00:24:44,333
"The enemy is the enemy,

474
00:24:44,432 --> 00:24:47,133
the enemy is the enemy."

475
00:24:47,232 --> 00:24:49,465
From Bellefontaine, Ohio, a doctor says,

476
00:24:49,566 --> 00:24:52,232
"Let us not condemn Lieutenant Calley

477
00:24:52,333 --> 00:24:54,633
"when it is the character of the war

478
00:24:54,732 --> 00:24:57,365
