1552
01:29:16,399 --> 01:29:19,533
But no visitor made more headlines

1553
01:29:19,632 --> 01:29:21,966
than the actress Jane Fonda.

1554
01:29:22,065 --> 01:29:25,399
During two weeks in the summer of 1972,

1555
01:29:25,500 --> 01:29:29,733
she broadcast at least ten
times over Radio Hanoi,

1556
01:29:29,832 --> 01:29:32,199
denouncing American POWs

1557
01:29:32,300 --> 01:29:34,666
for having committed war crimes,

1558
01:29:34,765 --> 01:29:37,265
urging the North Vietnamese to hold out

1559
01:29:37,365 --> 01:29:40,733
against American imperialism.

1560
01:29:40,832 --> 01:29:44,199
Many Americans would never forgive her

1561
01:29:44,300 --> 01:29:47,565
for what she did and said.

1562
01:29:47,666 --> 01:29:50,100
